title: 11/11/20 DPS-BEST OF

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP previews the 2020 Masters Tournament. Can Tiger shock the world again? How will Bryson DeChambeau's play translate at Augusta? We're joined by Sports Illustrated Senior Writer Pat Forde and Golf Channel's Brandel Chamblee. Plus, where will Chris Paul land?
